---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const title = "Airport Transfer Service Chicago | O'Hare & Midway Executive Transportation";
const description = "Professional airport transfer service for O'Hare and Midway. Flight tracking, meet & greet, and luxury vehicles. Corporate rates available. Book your executive airport transfer today.";
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-slate-800 to-slate-900 text-white py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6">
          Chicago Airport Transfer Service
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-300 mb-8">
          Professional O'Hare and Midway airport transportation with flight tracking and meet & greet service
        </p>
        <a href="/contact" class="bg-amber-500 hover:bg-amber-600 text-slate-900 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold text-lg transition shadow-lg inline-block">
          Book Airport Transfer
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Service Overview -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-5xl">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">Executive Airport Transportation</h2>
      
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
        Our Chicago airport transfer service provides seamless transportation between O'Hare International Airport, Chicago Midway International Airport, and your destination. Whether you're arriving for a crucial business meeting or departing for an important trip, our professional chauffeurs ensure you arrive on time, every time.
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 my-12">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-8">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">‚úàÔ∏è</div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">O'Hare Airport Transfers</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Serving all O'Hare terminals with complimentary flight tracking. Our chauffeurs know the most efficient routes and pickup locations for seamless service.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li>‚úì Terminal 1, 2, 3, 5 pickups</li>
            <li>‚úì 60-minute complimentary wait time</li>
            <li>‚úì Meet & greet at baggage claim</li>
            <li>‚úì Flight delay monitoring</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-8">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">üõ¨</div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Midway Airport Transfers</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Convenient Chicago Midway transportation with professional meet and greet service. Perfect for domestic business travel.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li>‚úì Domestic & international arrivals</li>
            <li>‚úì Curbside or baggage claim pickup</li>
            <li>‚úì Express drop-off service</li>
            <li>‚úì Real-time traffic monitoring</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 mt-12">What's Included in Your Airport Transfer</h3>
      
      <div class="bg-amber-50 border-l-4 border-amber-500 p-6 mb-8">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-lg text-slate-900 mb-2">Flight Tracking & Monitoring</h4>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          We monitor your flight in real-time, automatically adjusting pickup times for delays or early arrivals. No need to call or text‚Äîwe're already aware of changes.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-amber-50 border-l-4 border-amber-500 p-6 mb-8">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-lg text-slate-900 mb-2">Professional Meet & Greet</h4>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Your chauffeur will be waiting at baggage claim with a name sign, ready to assist with luggage and escort you to your luxury vehicle.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-amber-50 border-l-4 border-amber-500 p-6 mb-8">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-lg text-slate-900 mb-2">Complimentary Wait Time</h4>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          We include 60 minutes of complimentary wait time for domestic flights and 90 minutes for international arrivals, giving you peace of mind.
        </p>
      </div>

      <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 mt-12">Popular Airport Routes</h3>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h4 class="font-bold text-xl text-slate-900 mb-3">O'Hare to Downtown Chicago</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2">Average time: 35-50 minutes depending on traffic</p>
          <p class="text-amber-600 font-semibold">From $95</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h4 class="font-bold text-xl text-slate-900 mb-3">Midway to Loop/River North</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2">Average time: 25-35 minutes</p>
          <p class="text-amber-600 font-semibold">From $75</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h4 class="font-bold text-xl text-slate-900 mb-3">O'Hare to Suburban Offices</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2">Schaumburg, Oak Brook, Naperville</p>
          <p class="text-amber-600 font-semibold">From $85</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h4 class="font-bold text-xl text-slate-900 mb-3">Inter-Airport Transfers</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2">O'Hare to Midway or reverse</p>
          <p class="text-amber-600 font-semibold">From $120</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 mt-12">Why Choose Our Airport Transfer Service</h3>
      
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
        Unlike ride-sharing services or taxis, our airport transfer service provides predictable pricing, guaranteed availability, and professional service tailored to business travelers. You'll never wait in taxi lines, search for your ride, or deal with unpredictable pricing.
      </p>

      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
        Our chauffeurs are experienced professionals who understand the unique needs of executive travelers. They're familiar with all airport terminals, know the optimal pickup points, and can navigate Chicago traffic efficiently to ensure you arrive at your destination on time.
      </p>

      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
        For corporate accounts, we provide detailed receipts and invoices that include all trip information, making expense reporting straightforward. Monthly billing options are available, and we can integrate with corporate travel management systems.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 mt-12">Booking Your Airport Transfer</h3>
      
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
        Booking is simple: provide your flight information, pickup or drop-off address, and any special requirements. We'll handle the rest, including monitoring your flight and adjusting for any changes. You'll receive confirmation immediately, along with your chauffeur's contact information.
      </p>

      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
        For last-minute bookings, our 24/7 operations team is standing by. While we recommend booking in advance for guaranteed vehicle selection, we can often accommodate same-day requests based on availability.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-xl p-8 text-center mt-12">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Book Your Airport Transfer Today</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">Experience stress-free airport transportation with Chicago's premier executive car service</p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/contact" class="bg-amber-500 hover:bg-amber-600 text-slate-900 px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold transition">
            Request Quote
          </a>
          <a href="tel:+13129980909" class="bg-transparent border-2 border-white hover:bg-white hover:text-slate-900 px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold transition">
            Call: (312) 998-0909
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
